'''Trinn Reena''' was the founder of [[Reena's Interstellar Shipping]].

The local government of [[Chekkoo Province]] of [[Rodia/Legends|Rodia]], suffering from [[Grand Protector/Legends|Grand Protector]] [[Navik the Red]]'s embargo imposed against rival clans, hired Reena to [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggle]] illegal technology and [[weapon/Legends|weapons]]; for this, Reena had to find suitable parties for the job, free-traders and smugglers who could evade the Grand Protector's forces. Reena was promised a bonus for each group she could find.

Reena approached several individuals she found suitable, and, convinced they were interested for a challenging job, got into details about the political situation with the [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] [[Chekkoo clan/Legends|Chekkoo clan]] with a [[datapad/Legends|datapad]] with a local map and a rendezvous point with the officials. She instructed them to begin with smuggling some [[Power fence generator/Legends|power fence generators]] in order to be accepted by the Chekkoo.

